# Det Kollektive Klædeskab

## Tech Stack

- React 19
- Vite
- Tailwind CSS v4
- React Router
- Framer Motion (only when needed)
- Lucide React
- No backend
- No TypeScript

## Project Goals

Build a premium fashion rental website that feels:

- Modern
- Minimal
- Scandinavian
- Editorial
- Premium
- Sustainable
- Elegant

The website should feel like a luxury fashion brand rather than a typical webshop.

## Code Quality

Always prefer:

- Readable code
- Reusable components
- Small files
- Semantic HTML
- Accessibility
- Performance

Avoid unnecessary complexity.

Keep everything simple.